    <item>
      <title>通过消除对特权容器的需求来提高Istio Deployment的安全性</title>
      <link>https://www.servicemesher.com/blog/increasing-security-of-istio-deployments-by-removing-the-need-for-privileged-containers/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Sep 2018 16:22:22 +0800</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://www.servicemesher.com/blog/increasing-security-of-istio-deployments-by-removing-the-need-for-privileged-containers/</guid>
      <description>Red Hat OpenShift通过一个名叫istio-pod-network-controller的 DaemonSet 控制器将配置Pod的iptables规则的逻辑移出Pod本身，从而消除了特权容器的需求来提高Istio Deployment的安全性。</description>
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>Red Hat OpenShift发布Istio预览版</title>
      <link>https://www.servicemesher.com/blog/istio-on-openshift-technology-preview/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Sep 2018 16:09:49 +0800</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://www.servicemesher.com/blog/istio-on-openshift-technology-preview/</guid>
      <description>技术预览计划将为现有的OpenShift Container Platform客户提供在其OpenShift集群上部署和使用Istio平台的能力。红帽正在提供此计划，旨在收集反馈和经验，同时Red Hat期望在2019自然年提供OpenShift上Istio的全面支持和全面可用性。</description>
